            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/05/12/denver-public-schools-pay-216-million-to-wall-street-banks-to-unwind-swaps/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Denver Public Schools Pay $216 Million to Wall Street Banks to Unwind Swaps"><span>4</span> Comments</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/bank-of-america/" rel="tag">Bank of America</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">Bloomberg</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/federal-reserve/" rel="tag">Federal Reserve</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/jeannie-kaplan/" rel="tag">Jeannie Kaplan</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/superintendent-tom-boasberg/" rel="tag">Superintendent Tom Boasberg</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/wells-fargo/" rel="tag">Wells Fargo</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/05/12/denver-public-schools-pay-216-million-to-wall-street-banks-to-unwind-swaps/#comments">4</a> 
            </div><!-- .post-meta --></footer>
            
